{"tid":35250,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我就黎入到大學喇...迫不及待好想玩玩了","createTime":"2016-12-12T03:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T03:50:41.000Z","uid":35420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e50544acec29dd897a5de67600f11e61772d685c","tid":35250,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:20:41.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。 <br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。 <br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司權力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"683d7b87daecec86aaa452a5fdbc90db7c8280bc","tid":35250,"uid":10317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:21:21.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"e551b45dc132cb1bbc2bafa3d42b03d83a6b10a6","tid":35250,"uid":21746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:21:53.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"beb4ac0abceba8a0a3669c135c722c6f5b66f4c7","tid":35250,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b82361f99a28d2961714e75ae24e4a8c37a68f0","tid":35250,"uid":15993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:24:06.000Z","msg":"有無人知佢個nursing 讀成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d83c52de30b5c3403e5b366543a602efa75db1a","tid":35250,"uid":45650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:25:46.000Z","msg":"我記得你手臂幾粗下"},{"pid":"98dcf979af6e2dc47c478b2db58803b9c83d9a07","tid":35250,"uid":39630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:26:53.000Z","msg":"又回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src